    "description": "<i>- 有时我在想，这样做有没有意义……<br>- 意义？<br>- 换句话说，也就是目的？这一切的背后是否存在着起因？最后又会走向何方？<br>- “意义”……你得自己去寻觅。说不准稍加思索就能想出来。它就在你心里。<br>- 我不知道我能不能做到……唉，我甚至觉得自己还没准备好……<br>- 没人能准备好的。毕竟大家都是第一次。<br>- 第一次什么？<br>- 第一次活在这世上。</i><br><br>莉雅是一位正处于人生转折点的少女，被无聊又单调的生活压得喘不过气（有谁不是呢？）；某天却突然目睹了一场变故。她能适应新的事态吗？<br>风雨过后，她的存在又是否具有意义？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/513aa379eba28c2665a46adcb58a4e65.poster.avif?t=1674467514\" width=620 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/513aa379eba28c2665a46adcb58a4e65.webm?t=1674467514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/513aa379eba28c2665a46adcb58a4e65.mp4?t=1674467514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/0dbefcf5379f692ec661d49802e09b97.avif?t=1674467514\" width=263 height=67 /></span><br><br>踏上一段旅程，带领莉雅走过人生中最重要的时刻——它们能改变她的一生。<br><br>找出你的自我定位，发掘出你所背负的天命<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/b5adaacc8c4713f668e26616bf1bd5e6.avif?t=1674467514\" width=384 height=74 /></span><br>你的决定会对莉雅的一生施加深远影响——她的遭遇，皆看你的选择。揭晓路径和秘密。揭示你所做选择的结果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/449402749be2925182f6f6a6bea27fa0.avif?t=1674467514\" width=331 height=67 /></span><br>水面之下，暗流涌动。秘密层层相裹——它的核心隐藏在众多谎言和诡计之后，你准备好揭晓了吗？又能否发现真相？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/c1c6f122801a8876fd7f5e4b5285877f.poster.avif?t=1674467514\" width=620 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/c1c6f122801a8876fd7f5e4b5285877f.webm?t=1674467514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/c1c6f122801a8876fd7f5e4b5285877f.mp4?t=1674467514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/0484a256b142d517a01873ad799059ee.avif?t=1674467514\" width=459 height=75 /></span><br>莉雅可以与众多角色建立关系。他们每个人都独一无二，带领她游历不同地点，经历种种事件。你是会帮助她广识好友，探寻真爱，亦或独自走完这一生？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247740/extras/7e017d8d23353e1e6e7fdf4211fec0b8.avif?t=1674467514\" width=409 height=76 /></span><br>丰富的图像设计让众多角色和地点栩栩如生。探索充满细节和秀丽风景的奇幻世界。",
